# Description
# This file is the PPP file for the following modem:
# 		Skywire LTE CAT4 Verizon Modem: NL-SW-LTE-TC4NAG
#
# Instructions
# 	1. 	You will need to add your APN in the file: vzw-TSVG-chat
# 	2. 	This file is setup for PPP over USB. If you use UART, it will enumerate differently in /dev/.
#		Change the line:
#			/dev/ttyUSB3
#		to however the Skywire enumerates for you.
#

/dev/ttyUSB3
115200
connect "/usr/sbin/chat -v -f /etc/ppp/peers/vzw-TC4NAG-chat"
noauth
defaultroute
usepeerdns
local
debug
updetach
